    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Tylencholaimellus sinensis n. sp. A: Entire female. B: Anterior end. C: Anterior end showing amphid. D: Pharyngeal region. E: Expanded part of pharynx. F: Female genital system. G: Vulval region. H: Female posterior region." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212716/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212717>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Tylencholaimellus sinensis n. sp. Anterior region. B: Anterior end showing amphid. C: Expanded part of pharynx. D: Vulval region. E: Female posterior region. F: Female posterior end (scale bar A – D, F, G: 20 µm; E: 50 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212717/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

